        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>
                    <exhotlnk document="../afcs/AFC01914.pdf" bookname="AFC">Print ready (PDF file) copy of the AFC
                        letter
                    </exhotlnk>
                </para>
                <para>The engine oil pick up tube support mounting bolt and nut on front sump engines may have been
                    under-torqued on certain International DT466 and 530 engines. Inspect the bolt and tighten to 17
                    Lbf-Ft (23 Nm) of torque.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
